- Credit Card Application System with a user-friendly Tkinter GUI.
- User Authentication: Requires login before accessing the application form.
- Form Input Fields: Collects name, email, Aadhaar, PAN, income, credit score, education, requested amount, and card number.
- Input Validation:
    Email validated via an external API.
    Aadhaar and PAN formats checked with regex and digit checks.
    Card number validated using the Luhn algorithm.
- Credit Assessment: Calculates eligibility, maximum credit limit, and interest rate based on user data.
- Result Feedback: Displays approval/decline messages and credit details.
- Logout Functionality: Allows users to securely log out.
- Modern UI: Clean, styled interface using Tkinter and ttk widgets.
